1
00:00:00,190 --> 00:00:01,900
她还在说她的新工作
she was talking about her new job

2
00:00:01,900 --> 00:00:04,470
以及那本该是多么好的机会
and what a great opportunity it was going to be.

3
00:00:07,130 --> 00:00:11,820
兄弟姐妹  我如今把一件奥秘的事告诉你们
Brothers and sisters, behold, I tell you a mystery.

4
00:00:07,130 --> 00:00:11,820
{\an3}{\pos(374,247)}歌林多前书15:50

5
00:00:12,130 --> 00:00:14,420
我们不是都要睡觉
We shall not all fall asleep,

6
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,340
乃是都要改变
but we will all be changed

7
00:00:17,530 --> 00:00:22,160
就在眨眼之间  号筒末次吹响的时候
in an instant, in the blink of an eye, at the last trumpet.

8
00:00:23,090 --> 00:00:24,750
因号筒要响
For the trumpet will sound

9
00:00:25,470 --> 00:00:28,560
死人要复活成为不朽坏的
and the dead will be raised incorruptible,

10
00:00:29,270 --> 00:00:31,310
我们也要改变
and we shall be changed.

11
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:34,480
全能的主啊
Almighty God,

12
00:00:35,550 --> 00:00:39,410
您赐予您仆人的福爱  求您莫要忘了
remember the mercy with which you graced your humble servant.

13
00:00:40,190 --> 00:00:44,570
我们祈祷  您恩赐她进入圣徒的福地
Receive her, we pray, into the mansions of the saints.

14
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:48,470
我们的姐妹安息天国时
As we prepare our sister's final resting,

15
00:00:48,590 --> 00:00:51,770
愿主也垂怜她哀悼的亲人
look also with love on those who mourn

16
00:00:52,090 --> 00:00:55,070
赐他们以安宁
and give them comfort in their loss.

17
00:00:55,650 --> 00:00:59,850
我主耶稣保佑  阿门
Grant this through Christ, our Lord, Amen.

18
00:01:00,130 --> 00:01:01,260
阿门
Amen.

19
00:01:49,090 --> 00:01:52,780
-总统女士  能搭您的车吗  -当然
- Madam President, can I ride with you? - Of course.

20
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,740
{\an8}{\pos(101.6,102.65)}翻译   章鱼埃克斯

21
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,740
{\an8}{\pos(286,88.05)}时间轴   大葱

22
00:02:15,330 --> 00:02:16,780
{\an8}{\pos(114.3,241.15)}后期   饿得慌

23
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:19,160
{\an8}{\pos(121.4,101.15)}校对  草草

24
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:20,950
{\an8}{\pos(279.5,243.4)}顾问  老杜

25
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,580
{\an8}{\pos(100.8,98)}总监  草草

26
00:02:23,500 --> 00:02:28,000
{\pos(99,242)}原创翻译  双语字幕

